name: Leads Direct
overview:
Leads Direct is a new online service provider aggregation company and lead provider for multiple service-based verticals. Leads direct will be launching PropertyManagementDirect.com September 31st. PropertyManagementDirect.com will bring property owners and property management companies together with a focus in the following categories:

Residential Property Management
Commercial Property Management
Resort/condotel Property Management
Multifamily Property Management
Community Association Management

PropertyManagementDirect.com, Leads Direct’s flagship service portal will bring together property owners and property management companies in new ways. PropertyManagementDirect.com’s community approach to property management will offer an opportunity for property owners and property management companies alike to get answers to common questions, share management tips, receive and give advice on how to better manage property assets, and how to choose a property management company that fits the job.

For property management customers, look for advanced new features that meet your business needs with a focus on distribution options, budget management and more.
